---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout
  title="Amplified Event Strategy — Global Crypto Events Agency"
  description="The world's leading crypto events agency since 2015. We produce flagship Web3 conferences and experiences globally — from Solana Breakpoint to the Ondo Summit."
  bodyClass="home-page">
  <header class="container-fluid header">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="extra-lg-text">
          <span>GLOBAL EVENTS.</span><br />
          <span>EXCEPTIONAL</span><br />
          <span>EXPERIENCES.</span><br />
          <span>DELIVERED.</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="header-stats-outer">
      <div class="header-stats">
        <div class="header-stats-track">
          <div class="header-stat">
            <span class="stat-number">100+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Events Produced</span>
          </div>
          <div class="header-stat">
            <span class="stat-number">10+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Years in Crypto</span>
          </div>
          <div class="header-stat">
            <span class="stat-number">Global</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Reach</span>
          </div>
          <div class="header-stat">
            <span class="stat-number">Since 2015</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Industry Leaders</span>
          </div>
          <div class="header-stat" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="stat-number">100+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Events Produced</span>
          </div>
          <div class="header-stat" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="stat-number">10+</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Years in Crypto</span>
          </div>
          <div class="header-stat" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="stat-number">Global</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Reach</span>
          </div>
          <div class="header-stat" aria-hidden="true">
            <span class="stat-number">Since 2015</span>
            <span class="stat-label">Industry Leaders</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </header>

  <div class="container-fluid box-content box-content-short">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy c1-color">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <h1 class="title">GLOBAL EVENT<br />EXPERIENCE</h1>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="text">
                <p>We've produced events across the globe, giving us an extensive network of professional connections. Over our decades of experience both inside and outside of crypto, we've worked in Asia, South and Central America, across Europe and the United States.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy img-box">
          <div class="img"><img src="/images/work3.png" alt="" /></div>
          <a href="/work/Breakpoint2022.astro" class="project-link-full"></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid box-content box-content-short box-reverse">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy img-box">
          <div class="img"><img src="/images/work2.png" alt="" /></div>
          <a href="/work/Ondosummit2025.astro" class="project-link-full"></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy primary-color">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <h1 class="title">LARGE SCALE<br />EVENTS</h1>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="text">
                <p>We have produced some of the largest events for 11+ years—the longest standing crypto events producers in the business. We've run events as large as 8,000 delegates, with 500+ speakers and 5 venues concurrently.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid box-content box-content-short">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy default-color">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <h1 class="title">HIGH PROFILE<br />SPEAKERS</h1>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="text">
                <p>Throughout our careers, we have produced shows with major high profile speakers from Fortune 100 companies as well as Heads of State, members of congress, headlining entertainers, and more.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy img-box">
          <div class="img"><img src="/images/work5.png" alt="" /></div>
          <a href="/work/Hederacon2025.astro" class="project-link-full"></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid box-content box-content-short box-reverse">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy img-box">
          <div class="img"><img src="/images/work6.png" alt="" /></div>
          <a href="/work/Nearcon2024.astro" class="project-link-full"></a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <div class="boxy c2-color">
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <h1 class="title">TRUSTED & RELIABLE PARTNERS</h1>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="row">
            <div class="col">
              <div class="text">
                <p>We have worked directly with the founders from top projects in the space. Their trust in our team to deliver consistent results helps us maintain clients year-over-year.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="container-fluid default-content services-content">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col">
        <div class="lg-text">
          <span>OUR AGENCY SERVICES<br />& OFFERINGS</span>
        </div>
        <div class="normal-text">
          <p>We are a full-service events agency with global event experience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="services-accordion">
          <div class="service-item">
            <div class="service-heading">Production</div>
            <ul class="service-subtext">
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <div class="service-heading">Content</div>
            <ul class="service-subtext">
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <div class="service-heading">Sponsorship</div>
            <ul class="service-subtext">
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="service-item">
            <div class="service-heading">Event Planning</div>
            <ul class="service-subtext">
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
              <li>Bullet point placeholder text</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn-holder">
          <a href="/about" class="cr-btn primary">more about us</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>


</BaseLayout>
